{"tid":1450872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多區衝突13人傷 2人情況嚴重包括眼部受傷女示威者","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:05:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"137376e0e10b80faf8c3ea7620056b6221d44a3a","tid":1450872,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:53.000Z","msg":"多區發生衝突，醫管局表示，截至深夜11時半，有13人受傷送院，傷者17至56歲，其中2人情況嚴重，包括一名在廣華醫院留醫的男傷者，以及一名在伊利沙伯醫院留醫的女傷者。另外2人情況穩定，其餘9人經治理後已出院。尖沙咀警署外連續兩日爆發衝突，大批示威者昨日傍晚在警署外聚集，部分人投擲雜物及以激光照向警署高位的警員，警方多次從警署向彌敦道發放催淚彈，一名女示威者在彌敦道一個巴士站對出，血流披面，倒臥地上，現場所見，她右眼腫起流血，救護員到場包紮後將她送院。警方就表示，有暴徒向警署投擲汽油彈，引致一名執勤的人員雙腳燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-12 01:56:52"},{"pid":"55d51be5816d4f01faac6782ef63aec4aa09d186","tid":1450872,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:05:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入嚟投票啊<br />\nGoogle Form:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ae3aba46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdxZ4d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdxZ4d3.jpg&h=6c028dff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BiKvT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BiKvT3.jpg&h=4442e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62xOXy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62xOXy5.jpg&h=3d9717b6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}